name: Pemandangan 1
description:
taken around Pasar Senen. 
This is a typical photo that many photographers produce. Almost all over the world they travel and look for a place and take a picture of a landscape. This is done by professionals and amateurs with a variety of tools that can record images. Our eyes can't miss the slightest things that look beautiful and it's hard to perceive a different view than usual for us to consider beautiful.
